restaurant.name: La Kitchen - London
restaurant.description: From this fragrant little kitchen comes a mouth-watering array of Vietnamese delights. Their Pho noodle soups are a wholesome detox, with brisket beef and free-range chicken simmered to perfection over 24 hours – a deep, soul-warming broth.
restaurant.countrywide_allergy_warnings:
If you have any food allergies, intolerances or dietary requirements, please call the restaurant directly before placing your order.

They can answer any questions you have about the ingredients and cooking methods they use.

You can also find information given to us by the restaurant by tapping Restaurant notes.

To find out more about this restaurant’s food safety, visit the Food Standards Agency.
restaurant.allergy_warnings: You can find information given to us by the restaurant in Restaurant notes.
